{"tid":1828975,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Google 宣布停止支援 Chrome Apps","createTime":"2020-01-18T10:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T10:10:33.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"795621a311d14ccebe114c65208aee237fb2a70a","tid":1828975,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T10:32:27.000Z","msg":"Chrome 旗下的 Packaged Apps 應用程式平台於 2013 年推出，一直沒有太大起色。隨著網絡科技不斷改變，Google 自 2016 年宣佈從 Windows、Mac 及 Linux 的 Chrome 線上商店移除 App 項目後，就只剩下 Chrome OS 獨自供應 Chrome Apps。日前，Google 終於公佈將逐步停止支援 Chrome 應用程式，並公開其終止支援的時間表。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2540000/2544798/Google_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2540000%2F2544798%2FGoogle_1024.jpg&h=770d936b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n由今年 3 月起，Chrome 線上商店將不會再接收新的應用程式，而之前已經上架的程式則可以繼續更新直至今年 6 月。此後，Google 將完全停止支援 Windows、Mac 及 Linux 平台的支援，Chrome 企業版和教育版用戶則延長支援至年底。到今年 12 月，Google 將全面終止支援 Windows、Mac 和 Linux 的 Chrome 應用程式。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/20142612/browser-773216_1920-624x441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F20142612%2Fbrowser-773216_1920-624x441.jpg&h=1c3bac1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n明年 6 月，Google 將終止 NaCI、PNaCI 和 PPAPI API 的支援，而 Chrome OS 的支援亦會同時間結束。至於使用 Chrome OS 裝置的企業版和教育版用戶，支援服務就會延遲至 2022 年 6 月，此後就會完全結束支援所有 Chrome 應用程式。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2544798/Google%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4Chrome%20Apps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2544798%2FGoogle%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4Chrome%2520Apps&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKIV%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=681e45f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2544798/Google%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4Chrome%20Apps</a>"},{"pid":"58b62416c40de828d5ad7cef10c932f0cd16ef19","tid":1828975,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T10:33:45.000Z","msg":"值得注意的是，是次改動不會影響最廣受應用的 Chrome 擴充功能（Extension），Google 仍會繼續投放資源於所有平台的 Chrome 擴充功能。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/chromeapptitle-770x439_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2Fchromeapptitle-770x439_c.jpg&h=8eaa92fb&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nChrome 應用程式終止支援時間表如下：<br />\n<br />\n2020年3月：Chrome 線上商店停止接受新應用程式註冊<br />\n<br />\n2020年6月：除Chrome Enterprise和Chrome Education Upgrade用戶外，結束對 Windows、Mac和Linux的支援<br />\n<br />\n2020年12月：結束對Chrome Enterprise和Chrome Education Upgrade用戶的 Windows、Mac和Linux的支援<br />\n<br />\n2021年6月：結束對NaCl、PNaCl、 PPAPI API的支援<br />\n<br />\n2021年6月：除Chrome Enterprise和Chrome Education Upgrade用戶外，結束對 Chrome OS的支援<br />\n<br />\n2022年6月：結束所有Chrome應用程式的支援"},{"pid":"6f9866c09781017e478972d26dcace8ef5370e8b","tid":1828975,"uid":27432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T10:35:30.000Z","msg":"Google 做襯咩都爛尾"},{"pid":"773e478672c0db29f8f45e4ee300c33d914e2e6b","tid":1828975,"uid":80725,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T10:40:49.000Z","msg":"佢果D所謂既apps同條網址link有咩分別?點解我唔用bookmark?<br />\n利申: 唔識電腦"},{"pid":"37de60178a3a3a7709b565a708a44f5a843afa56","tid":1828975,"uid":35092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T11:21:46.000Z","msg":"冇左 PPAPI 即係話 Flash 正式收皮 ..."},{"pid":"b5a6aeaf601df4fb75e022f5a7abbf05d141211b","tid":1828975,"uid":328061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"773e478672c0db29f8f45e4ee300c33d914e2e6b","tid":1828975,"uid":80725,"like":7,"dislike":0